WEBVTT

00:02.068 --> 00:03.899
Previously on Boston Legal.

00:04.003 --> 00:05.528
It's time to start dating again.

00:05.638 --> 00:07.902
- Shirley's told me so much about you.
- Giggity-giggity.

00:08.007 --> 00:10.408
I met someone else,
and the night took a whole other twist.

00:10.510 --> 00:13.070
- I have been arrested.
- What for?

00:13.179 --> 00:15.443
- Impersonating a police officer.
- I'm such a loser.

00:15.548 --> 00:18.176
I want you to find out
if my daughter is using drugs again.

00:18.284 --> 00:20.514
- What time do you get off work?
- I get off at 7:00.

00:20.620 --> 00:23.851
I would appreciate your protecting
my relationship with her if you can.

00:23.957 --> 00:24.981
What about my relationship?

00:25.091 --> 00:27.559
- Night terrors?
- I haven't had them in years.

00:27.660 --> 00:30.891
- I'm afraid of clowns.
- Something screwy going on up there.

00:38.405 --> 00:43.536
And over 40% of the groundwater
in the United States- 40%-

00:43.643 --> 00:46.942
is contaminated by industrial,
agricultural, household pollution.

00:47.047 --> 00:51.381
Over the last five years,
hundreds of thousands of blood tests...

00:51.484 --> 00:53.145
given to Massachusetts children...

00:53.253 --> 00:56.381
have shown elevated levels
oflead in their blood.

00:56.489 --> 00:59.390
Yet what is our biggest fear?
The dirty bomb, not the dirty water-

00:59.492 --> 01:04.896
Objection. Mr. Shore is introducing evidence
that was never presented at trial.

01:04.998 --> 01:08.126
Nonsense, Your Honor.
I refer you to Plaintiff's Exhibit Number Apple.

01:08.234 --> 01:10.725
- I beg your pardon?
- Apple trash can is picked from God.

01:12.772 --> 01:14.171
- Huh?
- Mr. Shore-

01:14.274 --> 01:16.799
Not that you're 60,
but classic electrons are free.

01:16.910 --> 01:19.743
Objection, uh, I think.

01:19.846 --> 01:23.304
Mr. Shore, you have a notorious history
of courtroom theatrics.

01:23.416 --> 01:26.817
If your aim is to force a mistrial,
you will be disappointed.

01:28.388 --> 01:30.822
Pillow pants join forces
over embargo pylons.

01:32.759 --> 01:35.922
You aren't sailing past honor
for the liking of a room.

01:37.697 --> 01:39.927
These questions are birthday basements.

01:40.033 --> 01:42.934
To end the blue radish
is the upside of luxury...

01:43.036 --> 01:46.267
and sparking a good lizard
can only make tears fall in hindsight.

01:46.372 --> 01:48.169
Puddles do not ask for why not.

01:49.476 --> 01:53.173
It is cheese, breath and wind.

01:54.647 --> 01:56.615
It is cheese.

